            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Peto At<expan><ex>t</ex><abbr>ici</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nnorum</ex></expan> LXXX <lb n="3"/>et Meddil<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>coniugi <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nnorum</ex></expan> LX <lb n="5"/>Fortio &amp;lt;f=I&amp;gt;ilius <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Grabstele, oben abgebrochen. E mit zwei senkrechten Hasten wiedergegeben; Querhasten des F schräggestellt, L ebenfalls mit schräggestellter Querhaste. (B): Faust: Z. 2: At(ici).</p>
            </div>
